"And so,
the white night opened the door

00:17.160 --> 00:21.629
"and saw more gold and jewels
than he could ever imagine.

00:21.631 --> 00:24.081
"The wizard said,
'give me the princess

00:24.083 --> 00:27.418
"and you shall have
all the riches in the world.

00:27.420 --> 00:31.756
"The White Knight gazed upon the
wizard and saw it was the devil,

00:31.758 --> 00:35.760
who had already banished
the villagers' wives."

00:38.313 --> 00:41.415
"'I said, give me the princess''.

00:41.417 --> 00:43.234
'Never, he cried,'

00:43.236 --> 00:46.637
and slayed the devil
with his spear."

01:09.127 --> 01:11.545
Look after your sister.

01:21.339 --> 01:22.390
No!

01:22.392 --> 01:23.357
No!

01:23.359 --> 01:26.644
No! No!

01:26.646 --> 01:28.696
No! No!

01:28.698 --> 01:32.867
No! No! Help!

01:32.869 --> 01:35.319
Aah! Help me!

01:35.321 --> 01:37.371
Help!

01:37.373 --> 01:41.742
No!

01:46.030 --> 01:48.031
I don't know about this.

01:48.033 --> 01:50.668
Mike, will you stop
being a wimp.

02:09.721 --> 02:11.405
They say there's no escape.

02:11.407 --> 02:14.408
The demons will always
find you.

02:17.413 --> 02:20.865
Mike.

02:20.867 --> 02:22.583
Mike?

02:30.092 --> 02:32.443
Holy crap.

02:39.551 --> 02:41.719
Oh, my gosh, I am so sorry
for the delay.

02:41.721 --> 02:43.888
The system was down.
We overwork her.

02:43.890 --> 02:45.255
And I had to go into
the belly of the beast,

02:45.257 --> 02:48.526
who I affectionately
nickname Persephone,

02:48.528 --> 02:51.145
and do some machine
whispering--thank you--

02:51.147 --> 02:53.731
which is good, because
this one is a doozy.

02:53.733 --> 02:55.232
Emma Baker.

02:55.234 --> 02:57.902
38, math teacher
from Medford, Oregon.

02:57.904 --> 03:00.237
She went missing
17 days ago,

03:00.239 --> 03:02.907
and her body was found yesterday
afternoon at St. Baldwin's.

03:02.909 --> 03:05.826
St. Baldwin's is a now defunct
psychiatric hospital

03:05.828 --> 03:08.162
for the criminally insane.
Now, that is in Salem, Oregon,

03:08.164 --> 03:10.247
which is 230 miles away
from Medford,

03:10.249 --> 03:12.883
and we've been called in for
the bizarre nature of the case.

03:12.885 --> 03:13.968
Observe the photos.

03:13.970 --> 03:15.503
Wow. Look at that dress.

03:15.505 --> 03:18.005
Was she going
to a Renaissance fair?

03:18.007 --> 03:19.924
Not with her feet bound.
And missing persons report

03:19.926 --> 03:21.559
says that she was
in jeans and a T-shirt.

03:21.561 --> 03:23.460
But look at how
she's laid out.

03:23.462 --> 03:25.930
It's almost like it's a ceremony
and she's the sacrifice.

03:25.932 --> 03:27.565
There's obvious staging
going on.

03:27.567 --> 03:29.767
Could it be
a ritualistic killing?

03:29.769 --> 03:30.985
And cause of death
is still unclear.

03:30.987 --> 03:33.153
The M.E. report shows no sign
of sexual assault

03:33.155 --> 03:35.272
or mutilation except
mangled and missing fingernails.

03:35.274 --> 03:37.691
You know, there were rumors
of satanic rites being performed

03:37.693 --> 03:39.193
at Byberry Hospital
in Pennsylvania,

03:39.195 --> 03:40.945
which is also
an abandoned asylum.

03:40.947 --> 03:42.846
You know, judging by
all the graffiti,

03:42.848 --> 03:44.498
this place isn't
exactly locked down.

03:44.500 --> 03:46.148
Uh, yeah. The local P.D.
said that vandals and vagrants

03:46.173 --> 03:47.373
have been breaking in.

03:47.453 --> 03:50.037
Which means she could have been
killed elsewhere and placed here.

03:50.039 --> 03:51.655
She had limestone
under her fingernails,

03:51.657 --> 03:53.541
but limestone wouldn't have been
used when this asylum was built,

03:53.543 --> 03:55.158
so she was obviously
held somewhere else.

03:55.160 --> 03:57.878
Well, the bottom line is,
the unsub transported her

03:57.880 --> 04:00.264
hundreds of miles from
her hometown for a reason.

04:00.266 --> 04:02.016
We just need to find out
what that reasons.

04:02.018 --> 04:03.634
Wheels up in 30.

04:04.686 --> 04:07.021
Please!

04:09.124 --> 04:11.358
Tell me what you want!

04:14.947 --> 04:17.982
Oh!

04:17.983 --> 04:20.534
I'll do anything!

04:20.536 --> 04:22.152
No, no.

04:33.965 --> 04:35.365
Aah!

04:38.471 --> 04:41.972
Let me out of here!

04:41.974 --> 04:45.676
No! Aah! No!

04:45.678 --> 04:47.544
Let me out of here!

04:47.546 --> 04:49.346
Aah!

04:53.384 --> 04:55.352
Aah!

